acceptance_criteria: "Previous-version temp-project compatibility passes without data loss; release automation is locally runnable and daily-auto guarded; CHANGELOG.md and generated GitHub release notes reflect changes since v2026.5.12; telemetry/Sentry review is documented in ignored local ops notes; all local gates and GitHub release workflow are green; npm, npx, bunx, and GitHub release surfaces verify the published version."
