  "2026-05-14T18:15:39.331Z",codex-release-maintainer,"Duplicate-check evidence: ran pm context --limit 10,pm search release automation daily publish compatibility changelog --limit 10,pm list-open --limit 20,and pm list-in-progress --limit 20. Existing release items are closed; current request needs a new release chore under pm-rnpb."
  "2026-05-14T18:15:49.431Z",codex-release-maintainer,"Start: bootstrapped maintainer CLI (npm install -g .), verified pm --version 2026.5.12, node v25.9.0, pnpm 10.33.0, and pnpm build before release mutations."
  "2026-05-14T18:16:33.128Z",codex-release-maintainer,"Compatibility gate passed before release edits: node scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs --json used published base 2026.5.12, temp root /tmp/pm-cli-compat-D2WBlB, preserved 2 items before/after, validation_ok=true, health_ok=true, migration_warnings=[]; no breaking migration blocker found."
  "2026-05-14T18:32:47.634Z",codex-release-maintainer,"Evidence: full release gate passed after release automation hardening: build, typecheck, docs-skills, static quality, coverage (92 files / 1301 tests, 100%), version policy, secret scan, packed npx smoke (8 packages), npm pack dry-run, compatibility against published 2026.5.12 with item count preserved 2->2 and no warnings, and required telemetry/Sentry gate (finish_error_rate_pct=2.18, missing_error_rows=0, Sentry critical=1 high=4 under thresholds 10/20)."
  "2026-05-14T18:57:35.662Z",codex-release-maintainer,"Release evidence: local pipeline dry-run and actual push pipeline passed with required telemetry; release commit 73a704c and tag v2026.5.14 were pushed; GitHub Release workflow run 25878813780 completed green; main CI run 25878813752 completed green across windows Node 20, macOS Node 20, ubuntu Node 20/22/24; npm latest is 2026.5.14; public verifier passed npm metadata, npx, bunx, and GitHub Release metadata."
